eria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 66kg\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"a bout\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"battle\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday evening\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's participation at the Games has been the subject of intense scrutiny in some quarters after she was disqualified from last year's Women's World Championships for failing International Boxing Association (IBA)gendereligibility rules.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4803696833469545e-26, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's participation\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 361}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"intense scrutiny\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"some quarters\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's Women's World Championships\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"IBA)gendereligibility rules\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Khelif - who got the better of Hungary'sAnna Luca Hamoriin her quarter-final - has always competed in the women's division and has identified as female since birth.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hungary'sAnna\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's division\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024 The IBA have not divulged details behind Khelif's disqualification at the World Championships, though have repeatedly questioned the IOC's decision to allow the Algerian -and Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting- to compete the French capital this summer.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.8995764901396389, \"rank\": 0.11156614821991731, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.835660718281617e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.8584271179280756, \"rank\": 0.164890972665592, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9580509854916526, \"rank\": 0.027291251974804916, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9597274094911811, \"rank\": 0.02385301952832151, \"text\": \"French\