source/India_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Suwannapheng\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"her chances\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"their previous meeting\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have improved since then and I will fight with all I have got,' Suwannapheng told Thai newspaperKhaosod.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thai_people\", \"score\": 0.9711714113564518, \"rank\": 0.015967599021874515, \"text\": \"Thai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thai_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Suwannapheng\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have looked into it too, about her hormones, and I know she's lost to female boxers before, but that was a long time ago.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her hormones\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"female boxers\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am not sure if she's got stronger or if her male hormones have increased.'\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her male hormones\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suwannapheng added: 'But if we meet again, I am not afraid because we are evenly matched.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Suwannapheng\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have prepared my body well too, trained a lot.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think, no matter how strong or tough, we are both human, we both have two fists.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two fists\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Having come this far, I want to go all the way to the gold medal.'\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A defiantKhelif declared, 'I am a woman', after beating Hamori in her previous bout, withthe fighter's father coming forward to defend his daughter's participation at the Games.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A defiantKhelif\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"Hamori\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"her previous bout\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"fighter's father\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter's participation\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My child is a girl.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My child\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was raised as a girl,' Omar Khelif told French broadcaster BFM TV.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"score\": 0.9999865204337228, \"rank\": 1.3476055412728824e-05, \"text\": \"Omar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\"}, {\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9597274094911811, \"rank\": 0.02385301952832151, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http: